<HEAD>Eds: INSERTS 2 grafs after 5th graf, `Among the ...,' to UPDATE that
price paid for Pollock painting a record, comment from buyer; picks up
6th graf, ```Triptych May-June ...;' SUBS 7th graf, `Five sculptures ...,'
to CORRECT spelling of artist's name to Oldenburg, sted Oldenberg; SUBS
