sells to celebrities and others. PETER ROSS / Los Angeles Times; Photo, A 
detailed look at the decorated lapels of a vintage tuxedo, the specialty of 
Laguna artist Pat DeMar. ; Photo, Pat DeMar and her partner, Michael Laux, work 
on a tuxedo that, when finished, will be a unique dinner jacket, costing up to 
about $500. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
